<section class="wrapper">
  <div class="container py-[4.5rem] md:pt-24 lg:pt-0 xl:pt-0 xl:pb-24 lg:pb-24 md:pb-24">
    <!--/.row -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap mx-[-15px] !text-center">
      <div class="xl:w-9/12 lg:w-9/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] px-[15px] max-w-full !mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-[calc(1.305rem_+_0.66vw)] font-bold xl:text-[1.8rem] !leading-[1.3]  !mb-0 !text-center xl:!px-5 xxl:!px-10 !mb-3">1. Market Research – Identifying the Right Targets</h2>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">It all starts with structured research. We don’t buy lists or send mass messages hoping for a reply – we define clear search patterns to pinpoint decision-makers who actually fit your ideal customer profile.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap mx-[-15px] xl:mx-[-35px] lg:mx-[-20px] process-wrapper !text-center mt-9">
          <div class="xl:w-4/12 lg:w-4/12 md:w-4/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] xl:px-[35px] lg:px-[20px] px-[15px] max-w-full">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass-chart text-[#3f78e0] fa-4x mb-3"></i>
            <h4 class="!mb-1">Advanced search patterns</h4>
            <p>Using real-time data, LinkedIn Sales Navigator, and keyword searches, we refine criteria to find the best prospects.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-4/12 lg:w-4/12 md:w-4/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] xl:px-[35px] lg:px-[20px] px-[15px] max-w-full">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-globe text-[#e2626b] fa-4x mb-3"></i>
            <h4 class="!mb-1">Global reach</h4>
            <p>Whether you're targeting businesses in your region or expanding internationally, we adjust search parameters accordingly.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-4/12 lg:w-4/12 md:w-4/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] xl:px-[35px] lg:px-[20px] px-[15px] max-w-full">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line text-[#7cb798] fa-4x mb-3"></i>
            <h4 class="!mb-1">Data-backed targeting</h4>
            <p>Every lead is identified based on up-to-date company and role information, not guesswork.</p>
          </div>
          <!--/column -->
        </div>
        <!--/.row -->
      </div>
      <!-- /column -->
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap mx-[-15px] !text-center mt-9">
      <div class="xl:w-9/12 lg:w-9/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] px-[15px] max-w-full !mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-[calc(1.305rem_+_0.66vw)] font-bold xl:text-[1.8rem] !leading-[1.3]  !mb-0 !text-center xl:!px-5 xxl:!px-10 !mb-3">2. System-Driven Lead Identification</h2>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">Once the search criteria are in place, our system compiles essential prospect data:</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap mx-[-15px] xl:mx-[-35px] lg:mx-[-20px] process-wrapper !text-center mt-9">
          <div class="xl:w-3/12 lg:w-3/12 md:w-3/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] xl:px-[35px] lg:px-[20px] px-[15px] max-w-full">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-user-tie text-[#3f78e0] fa-4x mb-3"></i>
            <h4 class="!mb-1">Decision-maker names, roles, and company details</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-3/12 lg:w-3/12 md:w-3/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] xl:px-[35px] lg:px-[20px] px-[15px] max-w-full">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-building text-[#e2626b] fa-4x mb-3"></i>
            <h4 class="!mb-1">Industry, company size, and funding status</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-3/12 lg:w-3/12 md:w-3/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] xl:px-[35px] lg:px-[20px] px-[15px] max-w-full">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope-circle-check text-[#7cb798] fa-4x mb-3"></i>
            <h4 class="!mb-1">Verified business emails (when available)</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-3/12 lg:w-3/12 md:w-3/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] xl:px-[35px] lg:px-[20px] px-[15px] max-w-full">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-address-book text-[#ffb400] fa-4x mb-3"></i>
            <h4 class="!mb-1">Publicly available social and contact details</h4>
          </div>
          <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium !mt-2">While our system collects the data, our team manually reviews and refines the list to ensure quality over quantity. AI can assist in filtering, but every lead is checked by a real person before outreach begins.</p>
        </div>
        <!--/column -->
      </div>
      <!--/.row -->
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap mx-[-15px] !text-center mt-9">
      <div class="xl:w-9/12 lg:w-9/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] px-[15px] max-w-full !mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-[calc(1.305rem_+_0.66vw)] font-bold xl:text-[1.8rem] !leading-[1.3]  !mb-0 !text-center xl:!px-5 xxl:!px-10 !mb-3">3. Email Marketing as a Backup – Not the Primary Approach</h2>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">Email marketing is oversaturated. That’s why our main focus is direct outreach through LinkedIn and personalised engagement. Email is there as a secondary option - automated but targeted, used only to support the outreach process.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap mx-[-15px] xl:mx-[-35px] lg:mx-[-20px] process-wrapper !text-center mt-9">
          <div class="xl:w-4/12 lg:w-4/12 md:w-4/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] xl:px-[35px] lg:px-[20px] px-[15px] max-w-full">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope-open-text text-[#3f78e0] fa-4x mb-3"></i>
            <h4 class="!mb-1">No mass email blasts</h4>
            <p>We don’t send thousands of generic emails.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-4/12 lg:w-4/12 md:w-4/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] xl:px-[35px] lg:px-[20px] px-[15px] max-w-full">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-robot text-[#e2626b] fa-4x mb-3"></i>
            <h4 class="!mb-1">Automated but controlled</h4>
            <p>Emails are part of the strategy but not the main driver of results.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-4/12 lg:w-4/12 md:w-4/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] xl:px-[35px] lg:px-[20px] px-[15px] max-w-full">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-link text-[#7cb798] fa-4x mb-3"></i>
            <h4 class="!mb-1">Multi-channel approach</h4>
            <p>Email works best when combined with LinkedIn and direct communication.</p>
          </div>
          <!--/column -->
        </div>
        <!--/.row -->
      </div>
      <!-- /column -->
    </div>
    <!-- /column -->
  </div>
  <!-- /.row -->
</div>
<!-- /.container -->
</section>
